      "seed": 544897702,
      "version": 178,
      "versionNonce": 887335317,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776311924384,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Managing 100s of container \n2. Container need rapidly recovered \n3. VM down entire app down\n4. new version deployment nightmares ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Managing 100s of container \n2. Container need rapidly recovered \n3. VM down entire app down\n4. new version deployment nightmares ",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "vSg5N3qNcwbNPtTbFxLFC",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 10720,
      "y": 28820,
      "width": 682,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c0wQ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1800428922,
      "version": 316,
      "versionNonce": 1001727547,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776311924384,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. How to expose app FE to user & routing : Service Discovery \n2. Load balancing \n3. Resource Management -> allocating computer resource \n4. High Availability \n5. Security -> network policies \n6. Networking -> intercontainer communication \n7. Monitoring & Logging ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. How to expose app FE to user & routing : Service Discovery \n2. Load balancing \n3. Resource Management -> allocating computer resource \n4. High Availability \n5. Security -> network policies \n6. Networking -> intercontainer communication \n7. Monitoring & Logging ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "a1--b3gqzgNqW5ObarzEA",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 10700,
      "y": 29160,
      "width": 682,
      "height": 200,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c0wR",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 167139450,
      "version": 110,
      "versionNonce": 1648602869,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776311924384,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Kubernetes is an open source container orchestration platform.\nfeatures \n1. Container scheduling and placement\n2. Service discovery and load balancing\n3. Self-healing through automatic restarts and replacements\n4. Horizontal scaling\n5. Rolling updates and rollbacks\n6. Resource management and optimization",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Kubernetes is an open source container orchestration platform.\nfeatures \n1. Container scheduling and placement\n2. Service discovery and load balancing\n3. Self-healing through automatic restarts and replacements\n4. Horizontal scaling\n5. Rolling updates and rollbacks\n6. Resource management and optimization",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "tLbTsgh9pGyfW1xwDC6Ri",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 10700,
      "y": 29480,
      "width": 418,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
